    whyMatters: "In production, your API will fail. The question is: when it fails at 3am, can you figure out WHY? Structured logging means every log line is JSON — machine-parseable, searchable, filterable. A request ID threaded through every log line means you can trace a single request across 10 log entries. Health check endpoints let load balancers know if your service is ready. Prometheus metrics let you build dashboards and alerts. This is the difference between an app and a service.",
